  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The equation <math alttext=\"7 g plus 7 b equals 840\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>g</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>+</mo>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>7</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>b</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>840</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math> represents the number of blue tiles, <math alttext=\"b\"><mi>b</mi>\n</math>, and the number of green tiles, <math alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi>\n</math>, an artist needs for an <math alttext=\"840\"><mn>840</mn>\n</math>-square-inch tile project. The artist needs <math alttext=\"71\"><mn>71</mn>\n</math> blue tiles for the project. How many green tiles does he need?</p>",
